Carl Michael Ziehrer (more rarely spelled Karl Michael Ziehrer) (2 May 1843 – 14 November 1922) was an Austrian composer. 

Original C.M.Ziehrer Orchester

Francesc Masriera and Manovens - After the Ball, 1886.
